# Ajuste `@baseUrl`, `@buyerId`, `@productId` e `@orderId` conforme seu ambiente.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5073
@apiVersion = v1
@buyerId = 1
@productId = 1
@orderId = 1

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Listar compradores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Buyers
Accept: application/json

### Criar comprador
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Buyers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Buyer Teste HTTP"
}

### Atualizar comprador
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Buyers/{{buyerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{buyerId}},
  "name": "Buyer Atualizado HTTP"
}

### Remover comprador
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Buyers/{{buyerId}}

### Listar produtos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products
Accept: application/json

### Obter produto por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### Criar produto
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Produto HTTP",
  "description": "Produto criado pelo arquivo Web.http",
  "price": 129.90
}

### Atualizar produto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{productId}},
  "name": "Produto HTTP Atualizado",
  "description": "Descricao atualizada pelo Web.http",
  "price": 149.90
}

### Remover produto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}

### Listar pedidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders
Accept: application/json

### Listar pedidos por comprador
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders?BuyerId={{buyerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Listar pedidos por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders?Status=Processed
Accept: application/json

### Listar pedidos por intervalo de criacao
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders?CreatedFrom=2026-01-01&CreatedTo=2026-12-31
Accept: application/json

### Obter pedido por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### Criar pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "buyerId": {{buyerId}},
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": {{productId}},
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Atualizar pedido
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{orderId}},
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": {{productId}},
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

### Processar pedido
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/process

### Enviar pedido
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/ship

### Cancelar pedido
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}/cancel

### Remover pedido
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}

### Exemplo de erro de validacao: pedido sem itens
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "buyerId": {{buyerId}},
  "items": []
}

### Exemplo de erro de request: id da rota diferente do payload
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 999999,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": {{productId}},
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}
